name bold-extra
category Package
revision 79461
shortdesc Use bold small caps and typewriter fonts
longdesc Allows access to 'extra' bold fonts for Computer Modern OT1
longdesc encoding (the fonts are available in Metafont source). Since
longdesc there is more than one bold tt-family font set, the version
longdesc required is selected by a package option.
containersize 1448
containerchecksum 201f4267c64b24abf21b7d210e114929c9bdd6054439be9c64c4d9fe1bcc3932930f368e767cadba7e885fe612834f04e288b6e5812b627cc4fef77f48e22914
doccontainersize 217976
